{"id":"framework-decision-reversed","description":"Temporal supersession of a decision that was reversed: adopt then abandon a framework.","events":[{"ts":"2026-02-08T15:00:00Z","content":"We decided to build the new dashboard in Svelte for its small bundle size.","tags":["decision","frontend"]},{"ts":"2026-04-22T15:00:00Z","content":"We reversed the Svelte decision; the dashboard will be built in React to match the rest of the org.","tags":["decision","frontend"]}],"queries":[{"ts":"2026-03-15T00:00:00Z","query":"what framework is the new dashboard using","expectContains":["Svelte"],"expectAbsent":["React"],"hops":1},{"ts":"2026-05-10T00:00:00Z","query":"what framework is the new dashboard using","expectContains":["React"],"expectAbsent":["Svelte"],"hops":1}]}
